            "description": {
              "content": "Deprecated, use [Confluence's v2 API](https://developer.atlassian.com/cloud/confluence/rest/v2/intro/).<br><br>Returns inline tasks based on the search query.<br><br>**[Permissions](https://confluence.atlassian.com/x/_AozKw) required**:<br>Permission to access the Confluence site ('Can use' global permission). Only tasks<br>in contents that the user has permission to view are returned.",
